FROM properties_analytics
ORDER BY rent DESC
LIMIT 5;

# Real Estate Data Pipeline

## Overview
This project builds an end-to-end data pipeline using MySQL and Python.

## Features
- Extract data from MySQL
- Clean and transform data using Pandas
- Load processed data into analytics table
- Generate insights using SQL

## Tech Stack
- MySQL
- Python (Pandas)
- SQL

## How to Run
1. Setup database
2. Install requirements
3. Run pipeline.py

I designed an end-to-end ETL pipeline where data is extracted from a MySQL database, 
transformed using Python (Pandas) for cleaning and feature engineering, and loaded into an analytics table 
This enables efficient querying and reporting for business insights.
